Class BiomedicalEquipmentDAO

All Implemented Interfaces:
GenericDAO<BiomedicalEquipment, Long>
public class BiomedicalEquipmentDAO extends AbstractGenericDAO<BiomedicalEquipment, Long>
Data Access Object (DAO) for managing persistence operations related to BiomedicalEquipment entities.

This class leverages the generic CRUD functionality provided by AbstractGenericDAO, specifying BiomedicalEquipment as the entity type and Long as the primary key type.

It functions as a specialized adapter within the application's persistence layer, ensuring type safety and clear intention when interacting with biomedical equipment records.
